1. *Plašio* sam se mraka kad sam bio mali. (I was scared of the dark when I was little.)
2. Mama me je *plašila* pričama o babarogama. (Mom scared me with stories about bogeymen.)
3. Oni su se *plašili* da će biti kažnjeni zbog loših ocena. (They were afraid they would be punished for bad grades.)
4. Kada su čuli tu strašnu vest, svi su se *uplašili*. (When they heard that terrible news, everyone got scared.)
5. Da bi *preplašio* decu, tata bi se prerušio u čudovište. (To scare the kids, Dad would dress up as a monster.)
6. Uvek me *plaši* ta vožnja kroz tunel. (That ride through the tunnel always scares me.)
7. Sada se više ne *plašim* visine, naučio sam da se nosim sa tim. (I'm not scared of heights anymore, I've learned to deal with it.)
8. Životinja se *plašila* i pokušala je pobeći. (The animal was scared and tried to run away.)
9. Njegovi roditelji su ga *uplašili* da će ga napustiti ako ne posluša. (His parents scared him that they would leave him if he didn't obey.)
10. Ovaj film me je *preplašio* toliko da nisam mogao da spavam celu noć. (This movie scared me so much that I couldn't sleep all night.)